SUMMARY:Beginning Drop Spindle Spinning given by Nelly DeVault
DESCRIPTION:May 16\, 2026 1:00 – 4:00 PM. \n  \nParticipants will learn to make yarn of the oldest fiber arts tool in the world! When you leave\, you will take your first yarn with you. \n  \n$55 BSWG members \n$65 non-BSWG members students (includes one-year guild membership) \n$85 non-BSWG members (includes one-year guild membership) \n  \n  \nClass size 3-8 \n  \nMaterials provided by the instructor for an additional fee of $5. You may choose to buy your spindle from the instructor for $15\, borrow one for class or bring your own!  Spinning fiber provided. \n  \nNo experience necessary. \nTo register\, click here \n\n           Download QR
