BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Bloomington Spinners & Weavers Guild
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260613T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260613T160000
DTSTAMP:20260424T223050
CREATED:20251122T134352Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251122T134600Z
UID:5471-1781355600-1781366400@bloomspinweave.org
SUMMARY:All Ages Learn to Knit with Jen Richardson
DESCRIPTION: June 13th and 20th\, 1-4 pm \nAre you an adult or a creative kid (or know a creative kid) who has ever wanted to learn to knit?  Do you love having something to do with your hands?  Can you focus on a task for up to 30 minutes?  Fiber arts are really just fidget toys that end in cool stuff!  If that sounds good\, this is the class for you!  We’ll cover the very basics from the very beginning. \nIn this class\, we’ll learn knit stitches and purl stitches\, casting on\, and casting off to make some lovely coasters in garter\, stockinette\, and seed stitch.  We’ll talk about straight vs circular knitting needles\, and we’ll have a lot of time to work together and troubleshoot.  We’ll also talk about picking your next project! \nThis class is starting from the ground up\, so we’ll be knitting in the English\, or “throwing” style.  If none of those words made sense to you\, don’t worry\, we’ll cover it all!  This class is the place to start – we’ll define all those terms and more. \nIf your knitter is under 12\, they must have an adult with them for the duration of the class.  One registration fee is fine\, though. \n$30 BSWG members \n$40 Student non-BSWG member (includes one year guild membership) \n$60 non-BSWG members (includes one year guild membership) \nClass size 1-5 students (excluding adult helpers) \nNo experience required. \nA list of materials needed to bring will be emailed to you. \nTo register click here \n\n           Download QR
URL:https://bloomspinweave.org/event/all-ages-learn-to-knit-with-jen-richardson
LOCATION:Fiber Arts Center\, College Mall\, Bloomington\, 3038 East Third Street\, Bloomington\, IN\, 47401\, United States
CATEGORIES:Bloomington Spinners and Weavers Fiber Arts Guild Calendar
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bloomspinweave.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/image1-scaled.jpeg
ORGANIZER;CN="Bloomington Spinners and Weavers Guild":MAILTO:educationbswg@gmail.com, newsletterbswg@gmail.com
END:VEVENT
